plot: Captain Renard vows to kill Nick following the massacre in Nick's loft.

Neither Nick nor Renard understands how the captain was made to stab Bonaparte, apparently by Diana, but their hostility continues, now with official charges implying Nick's arrest, so he must hide at feral beaver Bud's. The healing Black Forest stick saved Nick, but may also be dangerous, as Eve's aftermath suggests. Despite being under police siege, Monroe wildly welcomes Rosalie's pregnancy announcement.—KGF Vissers
